subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text: {{Han simp|慶}} (elimination of bottom right component to {{l|zh|大}}) in the 1956 {{w|Chinese Character Simplification Scheme}} by the People's Republic of China. This character is not known to have existed prior to that. <!-- Refer https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/漢字簡化方案 -->
